---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Never Lose a Quote to a Slow Reply Again | Crystal AI"
  description="Free playbook: the follow-up system that closes more jobs using AI you already have. Built for HVAC, plumbing, and electrical contractors."
>

  <section class="band">
    <div class="frame lp">
      <p class="eyebrow">FREE PLAYBOOK</p>
      <h1>Never Lose a Quote to a Slow Reply Again</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">The follow-up system that closes more jobs — using AI you already have. Set it up in 10 minutes.</p>

      <a href="/downloads/never-lose-a-quote.pdf" class="cta-btn" download>Download the Playbook (PDF)</a>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-label">WHAT'S INSIDE</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>A Business Brief template that makes any AI sound like you — fill it out once, reuse it forever</li>
          <li>5 follow-up prompts that cover every stage from fresh quote to referral ask</li>
          <li>A correction loop that makes the AI get better every time you use it</li>
          <li>The math on why this matters — $14,000/month from emails you were already going to write</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-label">HOW IT WORKS</p>
        <p class="card-text">You paste a one-paragraph brief about your business into ChatGPT or Claude. Then you use the included prompts to draft follow-ups in 30 seconds. No coding. No new software. Just the AI tools you already have, working harder for you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="companion">
        <p>Grab the companion <a href="/prompts">Prompt Sheet</a> — 13 ready-to-use prompts you can print and keep at your desk.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-footer">
        <a href="/downloads/never-lose-a-quote.pdf" class="cta-btn" download>Download the Playbook (PDF)</a>
        <p class="fine-print">No email required. Just the guide.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .band {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .lp {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 150ms ease;
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .card-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .card-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .checklist {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .checklist li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .checklist li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .checklist li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .companion {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--paper-2);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .companion p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }

  .companion a {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .companion a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .cta-footer {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .fine-print {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>
